{"tid":293589,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[董建華][國有化]WSJ:中遠海運312億收購東方海外貨櫃航運 彭博未證實","createTime":"2017-06-22T09:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T01:56:42.000Z","uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f123a0283f874caf2b70658831c3e07e558799d","tid":293589,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T09:55:03.000Z","msg":"【傳中遠收購貨櫃業務】東方海外：不知悉任何併購<br />\n【本地】 2017/06/21 17:34<br />\n<a href=\"http://finance.now.com/news/post.php?id=329282&amp;type=local\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffinance.now.com%2Fnews%2Fpost.php%3Fid%3D329282%26type%3Dlocal&d=QdXelFQ4I9jJvmzBiBI9wu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=fec12e48\" target=\"_blank\">http://finance.now.com/news/post.php?id=329282&amp;type=local</a><br />\n【Now財經台】有傳中國遠洋海運集團收購東方海外國際(00316)貨櫃業務。<br />\n<br />\n據《華爾街日報》報道指，中遠海運正商討收購東方海外貨櫃業務，作價最少40億美元，折合逾310億港元，認為交易有助降低成本及提高運能。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，預期最快下月有正式公布。<br />\n<br />\n不過，據《彭博》引述東方海外表示，集團不知悉任何併購。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昨日 10:08 港股直擊 香港財經 中國財經<br />\n傳中遠312億收購東方海外貨櫃航運<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/stock/article/1589960/%E5%82%B3%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%A0312%E5%84%84%E6%94%B6%E8%B3%BC%E6%9D%B1%E6%96%B9%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E8%B2%A8%E6%AB%83%E8%88%AA%E9%81%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fstock%2Farticle%2F1589960%2F%25E5%2582%25B3%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2581%25A0312%25E5%2584%2584%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E6%259D%25B1%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E6%25AB%2583%25E8%2588%25AA%25E9%2581%258B&d=QdXelFQ4I9jJvmzBiBI9wu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=df4dfe10\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/stock/article/1589960/%E5%82%B3%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%A0312%E5%84%84%E6%94%B6%E8%B3%BC%E6%9D%B1%E6%96%B9%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E8%B2%A8%E6%AB%83%E8%88%AA%E9%81%8B</a><br />\n《華爾街日報》引述消息人士透露，中遠集團以至少40億美元(約312億港元)收購東方海外(00316)旗下東方海外貨櫃航運的談判已進入最後階段，交易最快或於7月達成。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，東方海外貨櫃航運的控股家族已經接受出售想法，雙方正磋商價格，可能最快下月便會宣布交易。<br />\n<br />\n中遠集團是全球第四大航運公司，市場份額達8.5%；至於總部位於香港的東方海外貨櫃航運則是全球第七大航運公司，市場份額為3.3%。<br />\n<br />\n東方海外由香港董氏家族持有。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEvergreen Is Happy Being Single<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/gadfly/articles/2017-06-21/evergreen-looks-single-and-happy-in-shipping-love-fest\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fgadfly%2Farticles%2F2017-06-21%2Fevergreen-looks-single-and-happy-in-shipping-love-fest&d=QdXelFQ4I9jJvmzBiBI9wu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=7541ce52\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/gadfly/articles/2017-06-21/evergreen-looks-single-and-happy-in-shipping-love-fest</a><br />\n<br />\nCosco Nears $4 Billion Takeover of Orient Overseas<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/cosco-nears-4-billion-takeover-of-orient-overseas-1497977963\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fcosco-nears-4-billion-takeover-of-orient-overseas-1497977963&d=QdXelFQ4I9jJvmzBiBI9wu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=9a680e26\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/cosco-nears-4-billion-takeover-of-orient-overseas-1497977963</a> <br />\n<br />\n華爾街日報：董建華家族賣盤　國企擬逾300億購東方海外業務 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E8%91%A3%E5%BB%BA%E8%8F%AF%E5%AE%B6%E6%97%8F%E8%B3%A3%E7%9B%A4-%E5%9C%8B%E4%BC%81%E6%93%AC%E9%80%BE300%E5%84%84%E8%B3%BC%E6%9D%B1%E6%96%B9%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E6%A5%AD%E5%8B%99/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2588%25BE%25E8%25A1%2597%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E8%2591%25A3%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%2597%258F%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E7%259B%25A4-%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BC%2581%25E6%2593%25AC%25E9%2580%25BE300%25E5%2584%2584%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E6%259D%25B1%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A4%2596%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%258B%2599%2F&d=QdXelFQ4I9jJvmzBiBI9wu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=a6